  "text": "More recently, however, the field has shifted to working on category-level pose estimation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . This presents many new challenges; most notably, the model must learn how the pose changes with the appearance of the object while simultaneously handling the intra-category variation of instances within a category.",
